At the mess table he sat silently , and drank a great deal . 
When full of liquor , he reeled silently home . 
When he spoke , it was to agree with everybody on every conceivable point and he passed through life in perfect ease and good humour . 
The hottest suns of India never heated his temper and the Walcheren ague never shook it . 
