I have served my King and country with honour . 
I was in Parliament for several years , where , I may say , my speeches were listened to and pretty well received . 
I don't owe any man a shilling on the contrary , I lent my old college friend , Jack Lazarus , fifty pounds , for which my executors will not press him . 
